1
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:10,680
Boss Fang told me to do it.

2
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,120
Which Boss Fang?

3
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,120
Fang Bing.

4
00:01:17,599 --> 00:01:18,560
He had his mistress

5
00:01:18,879 --> 00:01:19,480
