6
00:01:19,799 --> 00:01:20,879
to frame Manager Xiao.

7
00:01:22,959 --> 00:01:24,519
Actually, that day, Manager Xiao

8
00:01:24,519 --> 00:01:25,319
had ordered him to haul away

9
00:01:25,319 --> 00:01:26,120
the substandard angle steel.

10
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:27,920
But to cut his losses, Boss Fang,

11
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:29,560
after Manager Xiao left,

12
00:01:29,879 --> 00:01:31,000
had workers install it overnight.

13
00:01:31,599 --> 00:01:32,400
That's why...

14
00:01:58,319 --> 00:01:58,879
Hello

15
00:01:59,359 --> 00:02:00,280
Hello, Chairman Zheng

16
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,159
I've checked all the material logs

17
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:04,040
There's no record of them being moved

18
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,959
Please listen to this recording

19
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:07,959
It was Fang Bing

20
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:10,439
He had his mistress

21
00:02:10,879 --> 00:02:11,560
give me a sum of money

22
00:02:12,159 --> 00:02:13,159
to frame Manager Xiao

23
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:16,159
Actually, that day, Manager Xiao

24
00:02:16,159 --> 00:02:18,240
ordered him to remove the substandard angle steel

25
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,879
But to cut his losses, Boss Fang

26
00:02:21,639 --> 00:02:22,599
waited until Manager Xiao left

27
00:02:23,039 --> 00:02:24,319
then had the workers install it overnight

28
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,120
And that's how...

29
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,520
So that's what happened

30
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:29,520
Yes, Chairman Zheng

31
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,159
Xiao Yifan was wrongly accused

32
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,120
I understand

33
00:02:33,879 --> 00:02:35,319
I'll convene a meeting tomorrow

34
00:02:35,639 --> 00:02:37,360
Tell Xiao Yifan to attend

35
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,960
We'll play the recording at the shareholders' meeting

36
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:41,680
Yes, Chairman Zheng

37
00:02:54,639 --> 00:02:56,520
Do you realize how badly you've screwed up?

38
00:02:56,919 --> 00:02:59,719
He Junjie found out about the corner-cutting

39
00:02:59,879 --> 00:03:01,560
He's taking a recording to the company to expose you

40
00:03:01,919 --> 00:03:03,719
That He Junjie is too damn sneaky

41
00:03:03,719 --> 00:03:05,240
Can't we just pay him off?

42
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:07,120
Money can't solve this anymore

43
00:03:08,319 --> 00:03:09,319
Then just get rid of him

44
00:03:09,719 --> 00:03:12,199
Are you insane? Murder is a crime!

45
00:03:14,719 --> 00:03:16,240
Then what do you suggest?

46
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:25,960
Have Li Yao...

47
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:28,120
Have Li Yao take the fall for this

48
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,039
Why didn't I think of that?

49
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,879
Fine, I'll handle it

50
00:03:38,439 --> 00:03:39,159
Oh, right

51
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:42,479
He Junjie's recording

52
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,400
