53
00:03:48,719 --> 00:03:49,280
Hey, brother

54
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,280
Your case has been cleared up

55
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:52,360
Hurry back to the office for the meeting

56
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,759
Who was behind it?

57
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:54,719
Tell me now

58
00:03:55,319 --> 00:03:55,919
Where are you?

59
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,639
What are you doing?

60
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:20,759
Uncle

61
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:21,759
You wanted to see me?

62
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:25,920
Take the blame for this accident on behalf of Fang Bing

63
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,680
He'll pay you whatever you ask

64
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:29,879
What do you mean?

65
00:04:34,639 --> 00:04:35,360
This is from him

66
00:04:38,199 --> 00:04:39,079
I can't, Uncle

67
00:04:39,279 --> 00:04:40,600
With an accident this big

68
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,879
If I take the fall, I'm finished in this industry

69
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:46,439
You must bear all the responsibility

70
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:47,959
My mother is so sick

71
00:04:47,959 --> 00:04:49,079
I really can't afford to get into trouble

72
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,240
You fool

73
00:04:50,759 --> 00:04:52,480
Do you think He Junjie and the Chairman

74
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,240
won't figure out what caused the accident?

75
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,879
And you're the on-site safety supervisor

76
00:04:57,199 --> 00:04:58,399
Can you really escape this?

77
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,480
Why would I need to run?

78
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,879
Nobody died in this accident

79
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,439
The worst I'd get is suspension

80
00:05:03,879 --> 00:05:04,920
At most, I'll just tell the truth

81
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:05,920
and admit my mistake

82
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,079
You worthless idiot

83
00:05:08,399 --> 00:05:10,199
Can you pay back the money you've already spent?

84
00:05:10,639 --> 00:05:12,000
If you don't do it, am I supposed to?

85
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:15,759
Uncle, you're clearly setting me up

86
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,120
Just do as I say

87
00:05:17,879 --> 00:05:18,759
As for your mother's illness

88
00:05:18,879 --> 00:05:20,680
I'll get her the best hospital treatment

89
00:05:23,959 --> 00:05:24,519
Take it

90
00:05:33,319 --> 00:05:34,399
What are you doing?

91
00:05:40,759 --> 00:05:41,120
Junjie!

92
00:05:41,759 --> 00:05:42,480
What happened to you, Junjie?

93
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,079
Junjie!

94
00:05:47,079 --> 00:05:47,519
Stop right there!

95
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,639
Stop!

96
00:05:51,639 --> 00:05:52,399
Stop!

97
00:05:55,199 --> 00:05:57,240
Stop!

98
00:06:14,879 --> 00:06:15,439
President Fang

99
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,160
I got it.

100
00:06:18,759 --> 00:06:19,319
Good.

101
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,680
Junjie

102
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:46,600
Are you okay?

103
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,120
The recorder is gone.

104
00:06:58,399 --> 00:06:59,519
What's going on here?

105
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:00,759
What happened?

106
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:01,680
Han Lin.

107
00:07:02,399 --> 00:07:03,480
Tell Xiao Yifan and He Junjie to hurry up.

108
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,319
Why aren't they here yet?

109
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,240
Okay.

110
00:07:14,439 --> 00:07:14,959
What happened?

111
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,040
How did you get beaten up like this?

112
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,480
I'm fine, Chairman Zheng.

113
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:18,600
Just some minor injuries.

114
00:07:19,439 --> 00:07:21,000
Someone snatched my recorder.

115
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:24,160
In broad daylight! There's no law anymore!

116
00:07:24,639 --> 00:07:25,240
Did you call the police?

117
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:26,120
Yes, Chairman Zheng.

118
00:07:27,199 --> 00:07:28,600
Junjie had a very important recording.

119
00:07:28,759 --> 00:07:29,680
It could prove my innocence.

120
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,120
I've heard that recording too.

121
00:07:33,399 --> 00:07:35,600
So am I going to get beaten up when I leave too?

122
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,000
Everyone,

123
00:07:46,079 --> 00:07:48,040
the collapse accident is my responsibility.

124
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:50,279
I didn't follow Manager Xiao's instructions

125
00:07:50,279 --> 00:07:51,800
to remove the substandard materials in time.

126
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,040
That's what caused the company's losses.

127
00:07:55,439 --> 00:07:56,560
I'm willing to accept

128
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,720
any punishment the company gives me.

129
00:07:58,399 --> 00:07:59,279
Wait, that's not right.

130
00:07:59,279 --> 00:08:01,279
That's not what you said at the last meeting.

131
00:08:01,439 --> 00:08:02,040
Right.

132
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,839
Last month you pinned the blame on Mr. Xiao.

133
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,360
Fine.

134
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:06,680
Li Yao.

135
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,360
Chairman Zheng.

136
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,399
We're on a tight schedule.

137
00:08:11,199 --> 00:08:12,279
Internal company matters

138
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,759
shouldn't be spread around.

139
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,439
If the clients found out,

140
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,839
it could damage our company's image.

141
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,519
I hereby announce

142
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:28,199
today's meeting is adjourned.

143
00:08:28,439 --> 00:08:30,560
Take proper care of the injured workers.

144
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:31,920
Pay compensation where due,

145
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:33,399
and resettle those who need it.

146
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:34,879
Notify HR

147
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:35,799
to fire Li Yao.

148
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:38,080
Xiao Yifan

149
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,039
is officially reinstated.

150
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:39,720
He Junjie,

151
00:08:41,399 --> 00:08:42,960
you'll handle the materials ordering.

152
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:45,080
As for everything else,

153
00:08:45,799 --> 00:08:47,000
that's the end of it.

154
00:08:48,039 --> 00:08:49,919
After Xiao Yifan's reinstatement,

155
00:08:49,919 --> 00:08:52,080
through the efforts of real estate professionals,

156
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:54,279
developments sprang up everywhere,

157
00:08:54,279 --> 00:08:56,919
and prices rocketed skyward.

158
00:08:56,919 --> 00:09:01,639
The golden age of real estate had arrived.

159
00:09:03,399 --> 00:09:04,200
This Li Yao,

160
00:09:04,879 --> 00:09:05,759
he's a pitiful man too.

161
00:09:07,399 --> 00:09:08,639
What's there to feel sorry about?

162
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:10,080
He brought it on himself.

163
00:09:10,679 --> 00:09:11,360
Alright.

164
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:12,879
You two did well.

165
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,799
We got what we wanted at the auction.

166
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:17,559
Now let's discuss Plot No. 7.

167
00:09:18,519 --> 00:09:19,080
Chairman Zheng,

168
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,360
do you still remember

169
00:09:20,679 --> 00:09:21,960
before the land auction,

170
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:24,799
I discussed the pros and cons of Plots 6 and 7?

171
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:26,679
Of course I remember.

172
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,080
You said

173
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:29,799
Plot No. 6,

174
00:09:29,799 --> 00:09:31,440
sits right next to Phase Two of Wanhe Mansion,

175
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:34,279
which would push Phase Two's launch price

176
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:35,399
even higher.

177
00:09:36,039 --> 00:09:39,000
But the market is becoming saturated with high prices,

178
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,159
so the outlook isn't optimistic.

179
00:09:40,879 --> 00:09:42,519
Currently, Plot No. 7,

180
00:09:42,519 --> 00:09:43,720
doesn't offer good value for money.

181
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:44,840
However,

182
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,759
low-density high-end residences

183
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,200
or townhouses

184
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:48,960
would definitely be

185
00:09:49,639 --> 00:09:50,879
the top choice for successful people.

186
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,279
I deliberately had Han Lin

187
00:09:53,279 --> 00:09:55,399
deliver an authorization for 1.8 billion.

188
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:58,039
I didn't expect him to actually sell out the company.

189
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:02,080
So the two of you were putting on a show,

190
00:10:02,559 --> 00:10:03,480
and I was the only one in the dark.

191
00:10:04,679 --> 00:10:05,799
Seven years ago I already suspected

192
00:10:05,799 --> 00:10:07,120
that Han Lin was up to no good.

193
00:10:07,759 --> 00:10:09,720
After this auction incident,

194
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:10,879
I'm certain

195
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,120
he and the Fang Group

196
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:13,879
do have something shady going on.

197
00:10:15,039 --> 00:10:16,039
You're right.

198
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:18,320
Going forward,

199
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:20,159
you'll handle the Han Lin matter.

200
00:10:20,879 --> 00:10:22,279
For now, don't alert the enemy.

201
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:23,360
Yes, Chairman Zheng.

202
00:10:36,039 --> 00:10:37,039
President Su,

203
00:10:37,159 --> 00:10:38,320
you needed something?

204
00:10:39,679 --> 00:10:40,960
Yifan,

205
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,600
this is our company's

206
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,879
marketing agency proposal

207
00:10:50,919 --> 00:10:52,240
for Phase Two of Wanhe Mansion.

208
00:10:52,799 --> 00:10:53,879
I specifically printed a copy

209
00:10:53,879 --> 00:10:54,879
and brought it over.

210
00:10:55,919 --> 00:10:57,519
I've already seen the digital version.

211
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:02,440
I was worried a busy man like you might forget,

212
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:04,879
so I printed a copy to bring over.

213
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:07,320
Phase One sold so successfully,

214
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:09,919
