215
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:12,639
President Su,

216
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:15,120
Plot No. 6 went for so high,

217
00:11:15,639 --> 00:11:16,799
Phase Two will sell easily.

218
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:19,200
Many companies have approached me about sales.

219
00:11:19,879 --> 00:11:21,200
We'd certainly prioritize you,

220
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:23,679
however,

221
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:25,759
we're old friends, after all.

222
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:30,200
You know my strength and ability, don't you?

223
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:35,519
For the Phase Two marketing rights,

224
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,679
we plan to use exclusive sales,

225
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:39,480
requiring a lump-sum payment.

226
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,440
If you can accept that,

227
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,559
we can give you priority.

228
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:44,840
Sure.

229
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:46,360
As long as Phase Two goes to us,

230
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:47,519
money is not a problem.

231
00:11:48,759 --> 00:11:49,320
President Su,

232
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,600
this matter isn't settled yet.

233
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,200
We still need to discuss it in a meeting.

234
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:55,799
President Su,

235
00:11:57,559 --> 00:11:58,159
this way, please.

236
00:12:00,759 --> 00:12:01,480
Alright.

237
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:07,120
I'll be on my way then.

238
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,519
Xiao Yifan.

239
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:25,279
Why are you being so cold to me?

240
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:27,279
Have you forgotten

241
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:28,639
what we once had?

242
00:12:29,279 --> 00:12:30,320
Or are you deliberately

243
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,360
keeping your distance from me?
